headline: 3 Top Dividend Stocks I Can't Wait to Buy in April to Boost My Passive Income
summary: My top financial goal is to eventually generate enough passive income to cover my basic living expenses.  Vici Properties currently pays a 5.4%-yielding dividend.  At that rate, every $100 I invest into the real estate investment trust (REIT) can generate $5.40 of annual dividend income.
